<lb n="0296a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0296001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第九，【乙】高山寺藏古寫本，【丙】文和二年寫寶壽院藏本，【丁】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>大聖<note n="0296002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝大【明】【丁】，天歡喜＝歡喜天【乙】</note><note n="0296002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天歡喜＝歡喜天【乙】，天＝大【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296002"><lem>天歡喜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">歡喜天</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">大歡喜</rdg></app>雙身毘那夜迦法
<lb n="0296a04"/><note n="0296003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】＊，一卷＝儀軌【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0296003"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">儀軌</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0296a05"/>
<lb n="0296a06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0296004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…寺））三十七字＝（（唐北天竺））四字【明】【丁】，〔開府…智〕三十三字－【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0296004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑正號大廣智大興善寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】【丁】，〔開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑正號大廣智〕三十三字－【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0296004"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0296a07"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0296a08"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0296005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0296005"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0296a09"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0296a10"/><p><note n="0296006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔出陀…卷〕十三字－【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0296006" word-count="13"><lem><note place="inline">出陀羅尼集經第十一諸天下卷</note></lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296a11"/><p>身<note n="0296007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（曰）【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0296007"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296a12"/><p type="dharani">曩謨尾那翼迦<note n="0296008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【明】【丁】＊</note><app n="0296008"><lem><note place="inline">二<note n="0296009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔合〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296009"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0296010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瀉＋（一）夾註【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296010"><lem>瀉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">瀉<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app><note n="0296011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝迦【聖】</note><app n="0296011"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">迦</rdg></app>悉底<note place="inline">二合</note>母佉
<lb n="0296a13"/><note n="0296012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瀉＋（二）夾註【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296012"><lem>瀉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">瀉<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>怛&CB00135;野<note place="inline">二<note n="0296013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（反）【甲】，（引）【丙】</note><app n="0296013"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合反</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">合引</rdg></app></note><note n="0296014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佗＋（三）夾註【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296014"><lem>佗</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">佗<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>唵娜<note place="inline">去<note n="0296015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝音【聖】</note><app n="0296015"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app>下同</note>翼迦<note n="0296016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【明】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0296016"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>娜
<lb n="0296a14"/>翼迦<note place="inline"><note n="0296017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合＝四【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296017"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app></note><note n="0296018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尾＝毛【聖】，尾娜＝&M010527;囉二合【丙】</note><note n="0296018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尾娜＝&M010527;囉二合【丙】，尾＝毛【聖】</note><app n="0296018"><lem>尾娜</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&M010527;囉二合</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">毛娜</rdg></app>翼迦<anchor id="fxT21p0296a01"/><note place="inline">二合</note>尾娜翼迦<note place="inline"><note n="0296019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合＝五【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296019"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0296a15"/><note n="0296020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔怛囉二合〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296020"><lem>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0296021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（翼迦二合）＋簸【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296021"><lem>簸</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">翼迦二合簸</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛<note n="0296022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【聖】＊</note><app n="0296022"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>翼迦<note place="inline"><note n="0296023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合＝六【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296023"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">六</rdg></app></note>餉<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0296a16"/>佉<note n="0296024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝迦【丙】</note><app n="0296024"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">迦</rdg></app>悉底<note n="0296025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296025"><lem><note place="inline">二<note n="0296026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（七）【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296026"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">合七</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>餉<note n="0296027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296027"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佉迦只多扇<note n="0296028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【丁】＊，〔上〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296028"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">上聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>底迦
<lb n="0296a17"/><anchor id="fxT21p0296a02"/>囉<anchor id="fxT21p0296a03"/><note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0296029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【聖】【乙】＊</note><app n="0296029"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0296030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（九）【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296030"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">引九</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0296a18"/><p>心&CB00057;</p>
<lb n="0296a19"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0296031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）夾註【明】【丁】＊</note><app n="0296031"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>儗<anchor id="fxT21p0296a04"/><note place="inline">上</note>哩<note n="0296032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虐＋（二）夾註【明】【丁】，虐＝虎吽娑&CB00085;賀【丙】</note><app n="0296032"><lem>虐</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">虐<note place="inline">二</note></rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">虎吽娑&CB00085;賀</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296a20"/><p>心中<note n="0296033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296033"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00057;</p>
<lb n="0296a21"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0296034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）夾註【明】【丁】，〔唵〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296034"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0296035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虐虐＝虎虎【丙】</note><app n="0296035"><lem>虐虐</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">虎虎</rdg></app>吽娑<note n="0296036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【聖】</note><app n="0296036"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0296037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0296037"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note><note n="0296038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引二）夾註【明】，（引）夾註【聖】，（引一）夾註【丁】</note><app n="0296038"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg><rdg wit="【丁】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296a22"/><p>若欲作此天法。先須<note n="0296039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畫＝造【聖】</note><app n="0296039"><lem>畫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">造</rdg></app>像。或用<note n="0296040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝曰【聖】</note><app n="0296040"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>鑞<note n="0296041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">銅＝錭【聖】</note><app n="0296041"><lem>銅</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">錭</rdg></app>木
<lb n="0296a23"/>等及花木。若鑄若刻並得。其像形。夫婦二身
<lb n="0296a24"/><note n="0296042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝合【乙】</note><app n="0296042"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">合</rdg></app>相抱立。<note n="0296043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各長＝長各【丙】</note><app n="0296043"><lem>各長</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">長各</rdg></app>五寸。或七寸皆得。並作象
<lb n="0296a25"/>頭人身。造像不得<note n="0296044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">違＝還【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0296044"><lem>違</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">還</rdg></app><note n="0296045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">價＝像【乙】</note><app n="0296045"><lem>價</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">像</rdg></app>。<note n="0296046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（造）＋其【聖】</note><app n="0296046"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">造其</rdg></app>像<note n="0296047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成已＝或【丙】</note><app n="0296047"><lem>成<note n="0296048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296048"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>。當
<lb n="0296a26"/>以白月一日。於淨室內。用淨牛糞摩作圓壇。
<lb n="0296a27"/>隨<note n="0296049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝心【聖】</note><app n="0296049"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>大小。當取一升清<note n="0296050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔細〕－【明】，細＝淨胡【聖】【乙】，油【甲】，胡【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0296050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔細〕－【明】，細＝淨胡【聖】【乙】，＝油【甲】，＝胡【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0296050"><lem>細</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">淨胡</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">油</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">胡</rdg></app>麻油。<note n="0296051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296051"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0296052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＋（一）【丙】</note><app n="0296052"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">淨一</rdg></app>銅
<lb n="0296a28"/>器盛之。用上&CB00057;<note n="0296053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔文〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296053"><lem>文</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00057;油一百八遍。即<note n="0296054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暖＝煖【明】【聖】</note><app n="0296054"><lem>暖</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">煖</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0296a29"/>油。然後將像放著油中。安置壇內。用淨銅
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1266.0296b" n="0296b"/>
<lb n="0296b01"/><note n="0296055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">匙＝起【聖】</note><app n="0296055"><lem>匙</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">起</rdg></app>銅杓等率油。灌其二像頂身一百八遍。一
<lb n="0296b02"/>日之中七遍灌之。平曉四遍日<note n="0296056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">午＝子【聖】，中【乙】</note><note n="0296056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">午＝子【聖】，＝中【乙】</note><app n="0296056"><lem>午</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">子</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app>三遍共成
<lb n="0296b03"/>七遍。已後每日更&CB00057;舊油以灌其像。如是作
<lb n="0296b04"/>法乃至七日。隨心所願即得稱意。正灌油之
<lb n="0296b05"/>時數<note n="0296057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔數〕－【丙】</note><app n="0296057"><lem>數</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>發願。復用<note n="0296058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0296058"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>蜜和&CB00595;作團。及蘿蔔
<lb n="0296b06"/>根并一盞酒。及歡喜團時新花&CB00031;等。如是日
<lb n="0296b07"/>別取新者供養。一切善事隨<note n="0296059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝願【明】【丁】</note><app n="0296059"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">願</rdg></app>成就。一切災
<lb n="0296b08"/><note n="0296060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禍＝難【乙】</note><app n="0296060"><lem>禍</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">難</rdg></app><note n="0296061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉皆＝皆悉【乙】</note><app n="0296061"><lem>悉皆</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">皆悉</rdg></app><note n="0296062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">銷＝消【明】【聖】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0296062"><lem>銷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【乙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">消</rdg></app>滅。其所獻食必須<note n="0296063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＋（身）【乙】</note><app n="0296063"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">自身</rdg></app>食始得
<lb n="0296b09"/>氣<note n="0296064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＋（得靈驗故行者可用之也）【乙】</note><app n="0296064"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">力得靈驗故行者可用之也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0296b10"/><p>請召<note n="0296065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（&CB00057;）【明】【聖】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0296065"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">印&CB00057;</rdg></app>。以二小指<note n="0296066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【聖】</note><app n="0296066"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無名指。相鉤向內。即
