<lb n="0296c06"/><p><note n="0296107" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來去＝則去來【乙】</note><app n="0296107"><lem>來去</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">則去來</rdg></app>&CB00057;曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1266.0297a" n="0297a"/>
<lb n="0297a01"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline"><note n="0297001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（引）＋一【明】【丁】</note><app n="0297001"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">引一</rdg></app></note>鑠都<note n="0297002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＝魯【聖】</note><app n="0297002"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">魯</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note><note n="0297003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【乙】</note><app n="0297003"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT21p0297a01"/>羅摩馱&CB00135;曳<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0297004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑【明】【聖】，莎訶＝娑羅二合賀四【乙】</note><note n="0297004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎訶＝娑羅二合賀四【乙】，莎＝娑【明】【聖】</note><app n="0297004"><lem>莎<note n="0297005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引四）夾註【明】【丁】，（四）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0297005"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">娑羅二合賀四</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">娑訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a02"/><p><anchor id="fxT21p0297a02"/>誦七遍。但是誦&CB00057;人夢中驚怖。見諸畜生惡
<lb n="0297a03"/>境界等。當知是毘那夜迦王瞋。夢中覺已即
<lb n="0297a04"/>慚愧乞<note n="0297006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫＝真【聖】</note><app n="0297006"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>瞋。明日自有飲食勞謝。以水摩地
<lb n="0297a05"/>作二肘<note n="0297007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">水＝小【丙】</note><app n="0297007"><lem>水</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">小</rdg></app>圓壇。如<note n="0297008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">槃＝盤【聖】【丙】</note><app n="0297008"><lem>槃</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【丙】" resp="Taisho">盤</rdg></app>大亦得。即取<note n="0297009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03468;＝烝【明】，&CB14650;【聖】，蒸【丁】</note><note n="0297009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03468;＝烝【明】，＝&CB14650;【聖】，＝蒸【丁】</note><app n="0297009"><lem>&CB03468;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">烝</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB14650;</rdg><rdg wit="【丁】" resp="Taisho">蒸</rdg></app>餅五
<lb n="0297a06"/>顆蘿蔔根三顆火燒<note n="0297010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熟＝就【聖】</note><app n="0297010"><lem>熟</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">就</rdg></app>。有花著<note n="0297011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">花＋（者）【丙】</note><app n="0297011"><lem>花</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">花者</rdg></app>并燒<note n="0297012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝內【聖】</note><app n="0297012"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">內</rdg></app>
<lb n="0297a07"/>膠薰陸等香安於壇中。&CB00057;人<note n="0297013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔壇〕－【乙】</note><app n="0297013"><lem>壇</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0297014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西面＝面西【聖】</note><app n="0297014"><lem>西面</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">面西</rdg></app>向東
<lb n="0297a08"/>坐。誦大自在天&CB00057;一百八遍已。口云慚愧好
<lb n="0297a09"/>去。如是語已。壇中雜物<note n="0297015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盤＝槃【甲】</note><app n="0297015"><lem>盤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">槃</rdg></app><note n="0297016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛＝出【聖】</note><app n="0297016"><lem>盛</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">出</rdg></app>。出門向西棄
<lb n="0297a10"/>&CB00230;。西北亦得。口云薩婆藥叉<note n="0297017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（剎）【乙】</note><app n="0297017"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉剎</rdg></app>闍阿藹捨
<lb n="0297a11"/>訶<note n="0297018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝婆【乙】</note><app n="0297018"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>&CB00425;闍伽車。作是語<note n="0297019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297019"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>棄&CB00230;即<note n="0297020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歸＝婦【聖】，得【丙】</note><note n="0297020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歸＝婦【聖】，＝得【丙】</note><app n="0297020"><lem>歸</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">婦</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a12"/><p>大自在天&CB00057;<note n="0297021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0297021"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a13"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0297022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（引）＋一【明】【丁】，〔一〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297022"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丁】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毘<note n="0297023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跢＝哆【明】</note><app n="0297023"><lem>跢</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app>囉薩尼<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0297024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【聖】</note><app n="0297024"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT21p0297a03"/>囉<note n="0297025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝未【聖】</note><app n="0297025"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">未</rdg></app>唎達尼<note place="inline">三</note>瞋
<lb n="0297a14"/>達尼瞋達<note n="0297026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔尼〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297026"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">四</note>頻達尼頻達尼<note n="0297027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297027"><lem><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0297028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝婆【明】，娑【聖】【丁】，莎訶＝娑&CB00085;二合賀引【乙】</note><note n="0297028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎訶＝娑&CB00085;二合賀引【乙】，莎＝婆【明】，莎＝娑【聖】【丁】</note><app n="0297028"><lem>莎<note n="0297029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（六）夾註【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0297029"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">娑&CB00085;二合賀引</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">婆訶</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【丁】" resp="Taisho">娑訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0297a15"/><p>誦&CB00057;一百八遍。即心歡喜非但夢中。但覺有
<lb n="0297a16"/><note n="0297030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＝鬼【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0297030"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">鬼</rdg></app>事即作前法定<note n="0297031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好＋（也）【乙】</note><app n="0297031"><lem>好</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">好也</rdg></app></p></div1>
<lb n="0297a17"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" n="3" label="造像法"/><head><note n="0297032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">造像法＝造聖天像法【乙】</note><app n="0297032"><lem>造像法</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">造聖天像法</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0297a18"/><p>其像形端立。象頭人身。左牙出右牙折。面少
<lb n="0297a19"/>向左。其鼻向外<note n="0297033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00485;＝僂【明】</note><app n="0297033"><lem>&CB00485;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">僂</rdg></app>。有六臂。其左上手把刀。
<lb n="0297a20"/>次手把果盤。下手把輪。右上手把棒。次手把
<lb n="0297a21"/>索。下手把牙。造此<note n="0297034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">像＝象【明】</note><app n="0297034"><lem>像</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">象</rdg></app>不得<anchor id="fxT21p0297a04"/>違價。足數付之。
<lb n="0297a22"/>若鑄<note n="0297035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若刻〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297035"><lem>若刻</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>若<note n="0297036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畫＝盡【聖】</note><app n="0297036"><lem>畫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">盡</rdg></app>並得</p>
<lb n="0297a23"/><p>右此大聖大祕要法。人間希有。實勿傳之宜
<lb n="0297a24"/><note n="0297037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誡＝誠【明】【丙】</note><app n="0297037"><lem>誡</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">誠</rdg></app>慎也</p>
<lb n="0297a25"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>大聖<note n="0297038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝大【明】，〔天〕－【聖】</note><app n="0297038"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>歡喜雙身毘那夜迦法<note n="0297039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0297039"><lem>一<note n="0297040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下乙本奧書曰己亥之歲卯月十六日以御本交點了　加點了玄胤了，丙本奧書曰文和二年己亥二月二十七日於神護寺成身院書寫訖宣澄二十四歲，丁本奧書曰貞享四年中春十八夕一校點了淨嚴四十九歲元祿十五年十一月二十三日以御本再校了</note>卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丁】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
